  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\"><img alt=\"House Royce.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/50px-House_Royce.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/75px-House_Royce.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/100px-House_Royce.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Alayne Royce</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\"><img alt=\"House Royce.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/50px-House_Royce.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/75px-House_Royce.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/100px-House_Royce.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Alayne_Royce_by_nervouscunt.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rhaena Targaryen and Alayne Royce by nervouscunt.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/36/Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Alayne_Royce_by_nervouscunt.png/300px-Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Alayne_Royce_by_nervouscunt.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"415\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/36/Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Alayne_Royce_by_nervouscunt.png/450px-Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Alayne_Royce_by_nervouscunt.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/36/Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Alayne_Royce_by_nervouscunt.png/600px-Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Alayne_Royce_by_nervouscunt.png 2x\" /></a><div>Alayne Royce and Rhaena Targaryen by nervouscunt</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">House Royce</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Allard_Royce\" title=\"Allard Royce\">Allard Royce</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\nPrincess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a> <small>(rumored)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alayne Royce</b> was a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">House Royce</a> in the reigns of kings <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alayne_Royce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Alayne was plump and homely.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alayne_Royce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg/350px-The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg/525px-The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg/700px-The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Four-Headed_Beast_by_Warp_Speed.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/Four-Headed_Beast\" title=\"Four-Headed Beast\">Four-Headed Beast</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Elissa_Farman\" title=\"Elissa Farman\">Elissa Farman</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Samantha_Stokeworth\" title=\"Samantha Stokeworth\">Samantha Stokeworth</a>, and Alayne Royce, by Warp Speed ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Alayne was the daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Allard_Royce\" title=\"Allard Royce\">Allard Royce</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Runestone\" title=\"Runestone\">Runestone</a>. She became the favorite of Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>, who cherished her so much that she sometimes took Alayne flying on the back of her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Dreamfyre\" title=\"Dreamfyre\">Dreamfyre</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Aegon</a> and Princess Rhaena's <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">royal progress</a>, Alayne and <a href=\"/index.php/Melony_Piper\" title=\"Melony Piper\">Melony Piper</a> were the only lady companions of the princess who stayed loyal to her after King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> usurped the inheritance of Prince Aegon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Alayne arrived on <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a> at the beginning of <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a> for Rhaena's <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Rhaena_Targaryen_and_Androw_Farman\" title=\"Wedding of Rhaena Targaryen and Androw Farman\">wedding</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Androw_Farman\" title=\"Androw Farman\">Androw Farman</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> She stayed with the princess at <a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a>, where she, Rhaena, <a href=\"/index.php/Samantha_Stokeworth\" title=\"Samantha Stokeworth\">Samantha Stokeworth</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Elissa_Farman\" title=\"Elissa Farman\">Elissa Farman</a> became nigh inseparable and often rode Dreamfyre together. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Franklyn_Farman\" title=\"Franklyn Farman\">Franklyn Farman</a> dubbed the four friends, \"the <a href=\"/index.php/Four-Headed_Beast\" title=\"Four-Headed Beast\">Four-Headed Beast</a>\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Rhaena left Fair Isle upon the ascension of Lord Franklyn, Alayne came with her to her new court upon <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>. After Elissa betrayed the princess with her theft of Dreamfyre's <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_egg\" title=\"Dragon egg\">dragon eggs</a>, Alayne observed that the marriage between Rhaena and Androw had become loveless.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Alayne died at the end of <a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54&#160;AC</a>. At first, it was thought she had died of an <a href=\"/index.php/Illness\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illness\">illness</a>. Later, it was revealed that she had been <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poisoned</a> by Androw Farman, who was jealous of Rhaena's friendships with her ladies and weary of their mockery toward him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alayne_Royce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Allard_Royce\" title=\"Allard Royce\">Allard</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">Royce</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Hubert_Arryn\" title=\"Hubert Arryn\">Hubert<br />Arryn</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px